"use strict";(self.webpackChunk_N_E=self.webpackChunk_N_E||[]).push([[190968],{190968:e=>{e.exports=JSON.parse('{"slug":"careers","meta":{"title":"Hostel Brikette Careers - Hostel Jobs in Positano","description":"Join the team that values character and passion over a r\xe9sum\xe9. Explore dynamic opportunities and modern hospitality at Brikette Hostel in Positano."},"careersSection":{"title":"Be Part of Something Unique","section1Title":"Join the Team That Values You—Not Your R\xe9sum\xe9","section1Paragraph1":"At Hostel Brikette, we care more about your character, dedication, and genuine enthusiasm for hospitality than any formal qualifications. If you think you can provide our guests with memorable experiences through sincere kindness and a winning attitude, we want to hear from you.","section1Paragraph2":"Send us an email at hostelpositano@gmail.com and share what makes you stand out. Tell us about your past achievements—personal or professional—and how you\'ll go above and beyond for our guests. We\'re looking for engaged, energetic individuals who thrive in a people-focused, fast-paced environment.","section2Paragraph1":"We offer a benefits package that goes beyond standard hostel or hospitality norms. Think comfortable on-site accommodations, complimentary breakfast, cost-price access to our bar, and even free trips.","section2Paragraph2":"As a family-owned and operated business with a dedicated core team, we\'re excited to welcome fresh talent and new perspectives.","section3Paragraph1":"We\'ve built our own software to streamline operations, enabling you to focus on what really matters: delivering exceptional guest service. Routine queries are handled by our chatbot, so you won\'t spend your time answering the same questions over and over. And when processes do need your attention, our minimalistic, intuitive apps make it easy to learn and execute. We\'ll teach you everything you need to know, then step aside so you can shine.","requirementsHeading":"If you\'re interested in joining us, you should:","requirementsList":["Perform well under pressure","Be self-motivated, organized, and a strong communicator","Hold yourself accountable and stay hungry to learn","Be ready to roll up your sleeves and work hard","For full-time roles, you must be legally authorized to work in Europe for the entire duration of your employment"],"notGoodFitHeading":"You won\'t be a good fit if:","notGoodFitList":["You\'re a volunteer looking for a stay under three months"],"forCustomerFacingHeading":"For customer-facing roles:","forCustomerFacingParagraph1":"You should genuinely enjoy offering top-notch service to our guests. If you\'re not prepared to go above and beyond for people, this isn\'t the place for you.","rolesParagraph":"We\'re always on the lookout for dedicated cleaners (a full-time position), as well as team members for breakfast shifts, evening shifts, reception, and experience-led roles like hiking guides or boat captains.","closingParagraph":"If this resonates with you, send us an email at hostelpositano at gmail dot com with your relevant experience, the role you\'re seeking, and why you think you\'d be a great fit. We look forward to connecting with you soon!","section4Paragraph1":"Hostel Brikette began in 1995, back when Positano was more renowned for its fashion scene than global tourism. Our vision was to introduce travelers—especially younger ones—to the Amalfi Coast\'s vibrant charm. We started humbly, catering to the basic needs of explorers of that era.","section5Paragraph1":"Since then, Positano has blossomed into a premier luxury destination. In response, we\'ve modernized, adding new technology and amenities, enhancing our breakfast options, and creating a social atmosphere that keeps guests talking long after their stay. Many tell us Hostel Brikette is the highlight of their trip.","altAmenities":"Hostel Brikette\'s communal area","altProfessional":"Hostel Brikette\'s professional approach","altVintage":"Vintage view of Positano","altPanorama":"Modern view of Positano","apply":"Apply Now"}}')}}]);